graphics I have very little framre rate problems.  Missions are interesting now, they are closer to the terminal than before, and payout less because of it, but to balance that, the chests and mobs drop items on equal QL of the mission.  So if you do a 50% mission at level 30, mobs and chests will drop QL28-30 items.  Overall I make more money on missions now.<br>
<br>
Visually, nothing in the MMORPG world even comes close.  Funcom really made a huge beautiful world that is just as fun to run around and explore as it is to do anything else in the game.  I continually run into land features Ive never seen before and am blown away by it.  I'll never forget the first time I saw the notum cannons in Clondyke.  I sat there watching them fire off into space for at least an hour.  No other game can come close to AO in this department.<br>
<br>
Funcom has made some big errors with this game, but they have really cleaned up their act.  They are new to this, and I think they have learned a lot, and are a better company for it.  Those of us who have stuck it out are enjoying a really great game now.  If you are thinking about checking it out, you wont be disappointed. <p>**********************************<br>
*Chimaera lvl 60 Ranger - Officer of Triune<br>
*Kaellie lvl 38 Monk<br>
*Lisala lvl 51 MA of the Omni-Tek Dojo<br>
*Tomasin lvl 30 Enforcer<br>
